ex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616757\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616757\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wmv1665702630100.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wmv1665702630100.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wmv1665702630100.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wmv1665702630100\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      ExtendedSel\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether Windows multiple selection conventions can be used in a list widget. <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__section_w823ab1b5b1_w824ab1b5_w825ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__table_d12200e1_d12201e1_d12202e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__table_d12200e1_d12201e1_d12202e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__table_d12200e1_d12201e1_d12202e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmv1665702630100__table_d12200e1_d12201e1_d12202e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmv1665702630100__table_d12200e1_d12201e1_d12202e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The user can select multiple items using Windows multi-select conventions:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__li_d41624e1_d41625e1_d41626e1\">\n<p class=\"p\">To select multiple items individually, hold the [Ctrl] key down and\n                                 click each item to be selected.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__li_d41627e1_d41628e1_d41629e1\">\n<p class=\"p\">To select a contiguous group of items, hold the [Shift] key down and select the first item, then the last item.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmv1665702630100__table_d12200e1_d12201e1_d12202e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wmv1665702630100__table_d12200e1_d12201e1_d12202e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The user can select multiple items by clicking an item. Each clicked item is added to the selection, or removed if it was already selected.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__section_gxk_bp3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d163053e142\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__p_d103448e1_d103449e1_d103450e1\">To control the minimum and maximum number of items\n            that can be selected, do one or both of the following:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__ul_ebp_cp3_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__li_d41630e1_d41631e1_d41632e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__p_d103451e1_d103452e1_d103453e1\">Set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Syntax</span>\n                  to <code class=\"ph codeph\">REP</code>, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">REP(1-5)</code> (minimum is 1,\n                  maximum is 5)</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__li_d41633e1_d41634e1_d41635e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__p_d103454e1_d103455e1_d103456e1\">Set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field\n                     Interface</span> to use subfields, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">VC5(50)</code>\n                  (total length of the selected items must fit in the field length)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__p_d103457e1_d103458e1_d103459e1\">Although it is possible for the user to choose\n            multiple items, if more than the allowed maximum number of items is selected, when\n            leaving the field, the user will get the following error:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__pre_ibp_cp3_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">Error 0130 - Error on field\n &lt;FldName&gt;; too many subfields specified.</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__section_yr4_gp3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d163053e187\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__p_d108977e1_d108978e1_d108979e1\">This is a static property. It cannot be set in\n            ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wmv1665702630100__section_bhz_hp3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d163053e196\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rez1688451198680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rez1688451198680.html\" title=\"The ulistbox widget is a field-level widget that displays an open list in which one or more values can be selected. It can only be used in form components.\">ulistbox (ListBox )</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616757\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616757\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ExtendedSel Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ExtendedSel Determines whether Windows multiple selection conventions can be used in a list widget. True or False (default). Value Description True The user can select multiple items using Windows multi-select conventions: To select multiple items individually, hold the [Ctrl] key down and click each item to be selected. To select a contiguous group of items, hold the [Shift] key down and select the first item, then the last item. False The user can select multiple items by clicking an item. Each clicked item is added to the selection, or removed if it was already selected. Description To control the minimum and maximum number of items that can be selected, do one or both of the following: Set the Field Syntax to REP , for example REP(1-5) (minimum is 1, maximum is 5) Set the Field Interface to use subfields, for example VC5(50) (total length of the selected items must fit in the field length) Although it is possible for the user to choose multiple items, if more than the allowed maximum number of items is selected, when leaving the field, the user will get the following error: Error 0130 - Error on field <FldName>; too many subfields specified. Copy Using in ProcScript This is a static property. It cannot be set in ProcScript. Applies To ulistbox (ListBox ) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}